title: Pumpkin bread loaves
ingredients: ['2 (7g) sachets fast action dried yeast', '120ml warm water', '250g pureed pumpkin', '240ml milk', '50g butter', '50g caster sugar', '2 teaspoons salt', '1 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '1/2 teaspoon ground ginger', '1/2 teaspoon ground cardamom', '2 eggs', '800g plain flour, divided']
